# testcase-os — Cursor Instructions

See `_agents/instructions/shared.md` for project-wide instructions.

## Skills

Skills are located in `_agents/skills/`. Reference them in chat with `@_agents/skills/<skill-name>.md`.

Available skills:
- @_agents/skills/case-design.md — Design test cases from PRD
- @_agents/skills/case-import.md — Import Gherkin/Excel cases
- @_agents/skills/knowledge-import.md — Import business/tech knowledge
- @_agents/skills/case-execute.md — Execute test cases step-by-step
- @_agents/skills/daily-track.md — Log daily testing activities
- @_agents/skills/search.md — Search test cases
- @_agents/skills/jira-sync.md — Sync with Jira
- @_agents/skills/testrail-sync.md — Sync with TestRail

## Context

- @_system/active-context.md — Current sprint focus & blockers
- @_system/config.yaml — Project configuration
- @_system/tag-taxonomy.yaml — Tag categories
- @_system/context-map.yaml — Context loading rules
